Jim French (radio host) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_French_(radio_host) 0 James R. French (September 28, 1928 - December 20, 2017) was an American radio presenter and producer who has written and produced, as of 2011, over 803 radio shows, including The Adventures of Harry Nile and The Further Adventures of Sherlock Holmes series.
